CONSIDER

Usage:  consider <target>

This command tells you your approximate chances in combat against another
creature. Use it to determine how well you might fare.

Consider primarily uses the level of your target to indicate your chances of
success. However, it will also list any mitigating factors, such as immunities,
that will make the fight harder.

There are also several possible modifier tags:
 - hard: will require two players in the right level range
 - group: will require three players in the right level range
 - boss: will require four players in the right level range
