UNLOAD BOATUNLOAD

Usage:  unload <ship>

This command allows you to unload cargo from a ship at the docks.

See also: LOAD, BOARD, SAIL
#
USE

Usage:  use <item>

This command is used to interact with some items, such as the hestian trinket.
It also sets your active poison.

See also: HESTIAN TRINKET, POISON
